titleHowToImport: How to view/edit your previous Incident Report for Consumer
panelTitleHowToImport: Viewing or editing a previously saved Incident Report for Consumer
howToImportBullet1: From a blank form webpage (use F5/refresh to clear current form and refresh the page)
howToImportBullet2: Use 'Browse/Choose File' button on webpage to select previously saved .hcxs file.
howToImportBullet3: Directly below, click on the 'Upload Information' button.
howToImportBullet4: Previously saved information will be loaded into form.
howToImportBullet5: Edit, save and submit the information as desired.
